{"tid":714123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"只騙60多元的賤賊","createTime":"2018-06-23T12:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T12:29:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50a0906ecac195d3ad4e87dac0e6b7c1e2b42f41","tid":714123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180623/20428597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20428597&d=FiAKgoml5Zz3hpx%2Bxsr10aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bf27ccca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20428597&h=9d291f5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180623/20428597</a><br />\n<br />\n只騙60多元的賤賊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180623/large/e8904a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180623%2Flarge%2Fe8904a.jpg&h=98a0847f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《飲食男女》圖片<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有一回，在香港國際機場接機大堂的便利店，見到一名賤賊。老外個子不高，膽子不小，但胃口不大──他在便利店拎了3種飲料，排隊時先喝了一瓶水一罐啤酒，到了收銀處，撒野不付錢，掏出信用卡密碼又錯，人家要他現付，他沒錢，竟然囂張跋扈大聲叫罵：<br />\n<br />\n「你是不是中國人？」<br />\n一愕，此句倒字正腔圓。重複責問，反似是收銀的理虧，待慢客人──轉移視線，模糊焦點，不讓政棍專美。<br />\n<br />\n──但他明明是抵賴不付錢。飲料又喝進肚子中，沒記認，沒轍。<br />\n<br />\n他乘機奪回信用卡（不知真偽）逃走。2名女店員尾隨，他一輪嘴英語，2人不明，但如此明目張膽，怎能放過？幫忙找保安、報警的旁人也看不過眼。警察來了，先是2軍裝，後增至近10人（有揹背囊的學生型、年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n是機場「候命便衣」）。老外仍然「你是不是中國人？」一句走天涯──看來是慣犯，欺負過不少忌怕外國人的老百姓。<br />\n<br />\n警察喝令：「這裏不是澳洲、不是中國，這裏是香港！」澳洲佬扮醉、扮哭、扮惡、扮哀求，還嘗試偷走&hellip;&hellip;總之，我和朋友到樓上吃過晚飯後，一小時了，仍在擾攘？最後簇擁逮走。<br />\n<br />\n一場大龍鳳只騙港幣60多元──此賊好cheap！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n唔駛問阿桂 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n上海沒有姥姥 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"7f9d8cf6aa33c6321279921d28659258382dc1c2","tid":714123,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"Bogan#dog <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}